 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62371b3fe6670bb58c82e79184f1e09d95b369f","tid":313372,"uid":48817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:43:10.000Z","msg":"個艦長就fat fat 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淘寶十蚊貨賣幾舊水，今次唔知貪左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa6f4bbaeae61efb7ffc5c35060f971cc7d374c","tid":313372,"uid":122745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:47:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多野賣，呢架真係郵輪黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎黎到遼寧郵輪號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca711a936b0acb27c2eef0507668965f87ea86f4","tid":313372,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T10:55:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他指軍艦有中國特色</span><br />\n有乜中國軍事特色? 用二手嘢? 積木船?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">很感動終於有第一艘航空母艦</span><br />\n中國第一艘航母係明思克號囉ON9仔. 唔好同我講明思克號冇戰鬥力, 呢隻積木船一Q樣.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">ok啦，始終係國家嘅，美軍嗰啲係震撼啲係咪？</span><br />\n美軍個隻就係國家既.<br />\n積木船係黨既, 國家既軍隊同黨既軍隊都搞唔清."},{"pid":"930cf93e1087f1491adb17697c79a43a97184116","tid":313372,"uid":11753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:47:58.000Z","msg":"平心而論，去博物館唔買紀念品又講唔過去既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a6a44d524da753d215076f6683505415eed5be","tid":313372,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:55:49.000Z","msg":"美軍個隻就係國家既.<br />\n積木船係黨既, 國家既軍隊同黨既軍隊都搞唔清.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心水清<br />\n黨軍用來對付人民<br />\n自己計下軍警殺中國人多定美國人多"},{"pid":"92003d98978c55e84d04854b9d7410af3fbeee94","tid":313372,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T11:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美軍個隻就係國家既.<br />\n積木船係黨既, 國家既軍隊同黨既軍隊都搞唔清.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心水清<br />\n黨軍用來對付人民<br />\n自己計下軍警殺中國人多定美國人多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對人航母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d476a882e04ec8820976bfc36b8d37e18356ec1","tid":313372,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有樣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940bd50b7c354f20516d1f825990cf3136459b23","tid":313372,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:05:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁多野賣，呢架真係郵輪黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎黎到遼寧郵輪號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國最大海上購物城上線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1432552b673661ec0f4c8ea5c7549eea57465b0f","tid":313372,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T12:08:03.000Z","msg":"賭船 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s